datasets.name: b936e301
411e3f73
datasets.displayName: Proporção de Reparo (sem reparo no período)
queryLines:
SELECT
  in_study_repair,
  COUNT(*) AS qtd_veiculos,
  ROUND(100.0 * COUNT(*) / SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER (), 2) AS perc
FROM gold_fato_tempo_ate_evento
GROUP BY in_study_repair
ORDER BY in_study_repair;

datasets.name: dc63b2a7
datasets.displayName: Taxa de reparo por especificação spec_0
queryLines:
SELECT
  spec_0,
  COUNT(*) AS qtd_veiculos,
  AVG(CASE WHEN in_study_repair = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS taxa_reparo
FROM gold_dim_veiculo
GROUP BY spec_0
ORDER BY taxa_reparo DESC;

datasets.name: 9d058771
queryLines:
SELECT
  spec_0,
  percentile_approx(length_of_study_time_step, 0.5) AS mediana_tempo
FROM gold_dim_veiculo
WHERE length_of_study_time_step IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY spec_0
ORDER BY mediana_tempo ASC;

datasets.name: f8b1d715
datasets.displayName: mediana do tempo observado: spec_1 vs spec_2
queryLines:
SELECT
  spec_1,
  spec_2,
  percentile_approx(length_of_study_time_step, 0.5) AS mediana_tempo

datasets.name: 5dcba538
queryLines:
SELECT
  t.faixa_time_step,
  AVG(f.`171_0`) AS media_171_0
FROM gold_fato_snapshot f
JOIN gold_dim_tempo t ON f.time_step = t.time_step
WHERE f.`171_0` IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY t.faixa_time_step
ORDER BY t.faixa_time_step;

datasets.name: 075f7eea
queryLines:
SELECT
  dataset_split,
  class_label,
  COUNT(*) AS qtd
FROM gold_fato_snapshot
WHERE dataset_split IN ('validation', 'test')
GROUP BY dataset_split, class_label
ORDER BY dataset_split, class_label;

datasets.name: 8253753a
queryLines:
SELECT
  spec_0,
  spec_1,
  spec_2,
  spec_3,
  spec_4,
  spec_5,
  spec_6,
  spec_7,
  COUNT(*) AS qtd_veiculos,
  AVG(CASE WHEN in_study_repair = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS taxa_reparo,
  percentile_approx(length_of_study_time_step, 0.5) AS mediana_tempo
FROM gold_dim_veiculo
GROUP BY spec_0, spec_1, spec_2, spec_3, spec_4, spec_5, spec_6, spec_7
ORDER BY taxa_reparo DESC, mediana_tempo ASC;

datasets.name: ad86524a
datasets.displayName: Perfil de risco por especificação qtd veiculos >1 1
queryLines:
SELECT
  spec_0,
  spec_1,
  spec_2,
  spec_3,
  spec_4,
  spec_5,
  spec_6,
  spec_7,
  COUNT(*) AS qtd_veiculos,
  AVG(CASE WHEN in_study_repair = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS taxa_reparo,
  percentile_approx(length_of_study_time_step, 0.5) AS mediana_tempo
FROM gold_dim_veiculo
GROUP BY spec_0, spec_1, spec_2, spec_3, spec_4, spec_5, spec_6, spec_7
HAVING COUNT(*) > 10
ORDER BY taxa_reparo DESC, mediana_tempo ASC;
